          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/06/15595270/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_3630737002351205007.png",
                "id": "talent86165",
                "key": "The Classic of Acupuncture",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "The Classic of Acupuncture"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Gossamer Sprite.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/06/15595270/02943d17a2ad29f325fdac70651d2bae_3428514032512628453.png",
                "id": "talent95195",
                "key": "Universal Diagnosis",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Universal Diagnosis"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pulsing Clarity</span> dan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seamless Shield.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pulsing Clarity</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Tahap Aksi dimulai:</span> Menciptakan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Seamless Shield</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Seamless Shield</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p>Memberikan 1 poin Perisai untuk melindungi Karakter aktifmu. </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat efek ini dihapus atau diciptakan kembali:</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span> dan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter aktifmu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/06/15595270/ed10b8e3def17c518055b3421bfcb94a_582866635012455000.png",
                "id": "talent75923",
                "key": "Holistic Revivification",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Holistic Revivification"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #99FF88\">Dendro DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\"> </span>dan memulihkan 1 poin HP Karakter Aktifmu.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/06/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2628401900603468866.png",
                "id": "talent53002",
                "key": "Gossamer Sprite",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/06/15595270/a3d29e698acee488ea48e7cd36af0835_7093387002577718367.png",
                "title": "Gossamer Sprite"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Dendro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG ke kasus Pyro atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, membuat [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] yang akan mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG di akhir Ronde (Jumlah penggunaan 1 kali, maksimum 2 tumpukan)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/06/15595270/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_3623800798757279339.png",
                "id": "talent55755",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Perisai</span></strong></p><p>Saat Karakter yang dilindungi Perisai menerima DMG, Perisai akan terkonsumsi untuk menahan DMG yang diterima.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/06/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7261065017109175236.png",
